Encore Capital LLP: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 24, 2017 11:51 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Encore Capital LLP



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Encore Capital LLP is a private equity firm specializing in emerging growth, growth capital, management buy-outs, management buy-ins, institutional buy-outs and development capital (replacement, expansion and acquisition) transactions. It seeks to invest in leisure facilities, capital goods, building products, service companies in unquoted (and sometimes quoted)UK companies. It typically seeks to invest between £1 million ($1.56 million) and £10 million ($15.64 million) with the target EBITDA between £0.75 million ($0.95 million) and £2.5 million ($3.81 million). The firm prefers to take majority stake. It invest from its personal capital and from balance sheet and is typically invested for ...
Encore Capital LLP is a private equity firm specializing in emerging growth, growth capital, management buy-outs, management buy-ins, institutional buy-outs and development capital (replacement, expansion and acquisition) transactions. It seeks to invest in leisure facilities, capital goods, building products, service companies in unquoted (and sometimes quoted)UK companies. It typically seeks to invest between £1 million ($1.56 million) and £10 million ($15.64 million) with the target EBITDA between £0.75 million ($0.95 million) and £2.5 million ($3.81 million). The firm prefers to take majority stake. It invest from its personal capital and from balance sheet and is typically invested for four to five years. Encore Capital LLP is based in London, United Kingdom.
Detailed Description


