Careers

Choosing a Career with Encore Capital Group
Should you choose to pursue a career with Encore Capital and its subsidiaries (collectively, the “Company”), we are ready to partner with you to shape your future. As an organization, we are defined by deep investments in data and analytics, a strong entrepreneurial spirit, and an authentic commitment to partnering with our consumers. We seek candidates with a proven track record of accomplishment and a commitment to extraordinary performance.
Developing Top Talent
Our leaders are committed to developing talent and work to maximize business results through the aspirations, knowledge, and skills of our team.
Balancing Personal and Professional Goals
In addition to top-notch compensation structures, the Company offers employee programs that promote personal and professional goals such as leadership and skills training, tuition assistance in support of continued edition, wellness initiatives that have earned Encore recognition as one of San Diego’s Healthiest Employers, and active community outreach.
We firmly believe in work-life balance, are committed to healthy living, and actively promote personal and professional satisfaction.


Note: Our Career Opportunities page is for individuals seeking employment opportunities with Encore Capital Group. Staffing agencies and individuals being represented by an agency are not authorized to use this site or to submit profiles or resumes. Any such submissions will be considered unsolicited. Encore Capital Group does not accept unsolicited resumes, profiles or applications from agencies. Encore Capital Group is not responsible for any fees related to unsolicited resumes, profiles or applications.



   







