Consumer Testimonials
Midland Credit Management
Midland Funding LLC



Consumers

Who is Midland Credit Management?
If you are one of our consumers, you probably know us as Midland Credit Management (or MCM). Midland Credit Management, a subsidiary of Encore Capital Group, works with consumers to resolve past-due obligations. MCM services accounts after the originating creditor has charged-off the account. Whether you are looking for a payment plan, discount, or a custom solution, we are here to help.
With over 2,000 highly trained and professional account managers, we are prepared to develop a customized solution for you. We have a long history of integrity and fair dealing, and we will work closely with you to resolve your obligations.
We have created the industry’s first Consumer Bill of Rights, which details our commitment to conduct business ethically and in ways that support consumers’ financial recovery.
Have you heard from MCM?
If you have heard from MCM, your obligation to a lender is now your obligation to Midland Funding, LLC. Please give us a call at 1-877-240-2377 or visit online to learn about your options or discuss your account.
Please understand that Midland Credit Management is a debt collector. Midland Credit Management’s communications with consumers are an attempt to collect a debt. Any information we obtain will be used for that purpose.



   







