Encore Capital Group

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search






A major contributor to this article appears to have a close connection with its subject. It may require cleanup to comply with Wikipedia's content policies, particularly neutral point of view. Please discuss further on the talk page. (March 2012) (Learn how and when to remove this template message)



Encore Capital Group





Type

Public


Traded as
